snippet.title: Adidas Power Soccer PS1 Playthrough - How Much Did Adidas Pay For This
snippet.description:
Adidas Power Soccer is a football simulation video game developed and published by British developer Psygnosis and sponsored by German sportswear company Adidas. Released in 1996, the game launched versions for PlayStation and Windows. 

Initial Release Date: June 1996

Developer: Psygnosis
Publisher: Psygnosis

Platforms: Microsoft Windows, Playstation

Series: Adidas Power Soccer

#adidas #ps1 #gaming #playthrough #football
